  <name>Win2xcur</name>
  <summary>Convert Windows cursors to Xcursor</summary>
  <description>
    <p>Win2xcur is a tool that converts Windows cursor themes (.cur, .ani files) to Xcursor format for use on Linux systems.</p>
    <p>Features:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Convert individual cursor files or entire cursor themes</li>
      <li>Support for both static (.cur) and animated (.ani) cursors</li>
      <li>Preview cursors before conversion</li>
      <li>Easy to use graphical interface</li>
    </ul>
  </description>

  <developer id="io.github.ayasa520">
    <name>ayasa520</name>
  </developer>

